{
  "stem": "19231.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they asked me, you have a passport?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they said, well, you have to take out a passport, become a citizen, then you can have a job.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I took out a Russian passport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I got the job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "How old were you, Sala?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 16 and 1/2.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All alone.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All alone.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not one-- and we were such big families.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From my mother's side, so many cousins, uncles-- all alone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was what you feared the most.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was hard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So they gave me a place where to, you know, where the factory was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not too far away, they build like barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- and they give us to live there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're called [NON-ENGLISH], like a dormitory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that-- that was we only had a little bed, a little chair.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the floor was still ground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They build up so it's, you know, barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were a lot of people that were evacuated even from Russia, like people from Krakow-- no, Krakow is Poland-- from the Zamost, from Kharkov, from Bessarabia, from Romania.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a big, big one place that we were all together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them had sisters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of them had a mom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was all alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- we made friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was one girl from Lodz, from Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was a little older than I am.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were all-- all made-- we were all close.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We all worked many hours.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I used to work night shift.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And for me to sleep in the daytime was so hard, because one came in and one screamed and one talked.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was impossible to sleep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we had to go at night to work, it was so hard.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
